properties.label:description: The label collection represent polygons from the BLM FOIVEG_POLY feature class, a detailed classification  of vegetation that covers forested lands in detail and non-forest lands with broad and general classifications.  It includes related table data from the MicroStorms (MS) system to describe forest vegetation and delineates  polygons primarily based on differences in vegetative cover, size, and age. FOIVEG_POLY attributes describe  both the overall forest stand as well as the layers within that stand, including cover type and ten-year age class.
